{"tid":789108,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網購亞麻籽油竟「含大麻」 瘋生酮飲食熟女無辜遭法辦","createTime":"2018-08-22T04:04:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T04:36:06.000Z","uid":13468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d3a49fc48e456a95cf47396460408548987d428c","tid":789108,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T04:04:48.000Z","msg":"網購亞麻籽油竟「含大麻」 瘋生酮飲食熟女無辜遭法辦<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/2521887\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F2521887&d=0nlo1NHfRPJ8d1%2BNnXxxC%2FM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=7fe675c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F2521887&h=29c998d8\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/2521887</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_2521887_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_2521887_1.jpg&h=f04a66ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉女透過美國「iHerb」網站購買亞麻籽油，未料商品去年9月入關時卻被查出有大麻成分。（擷取自iHerb網站）<br />\n<br />\n〔記者陳慰慈／新北報導〕新北市40多歲的劉姓熟女為了身體健康，接觸「生酮飲食」，開始喝食用油，但坊間食用油價格較高，劉女於是透過美國「iHerb」網站購買便宜的亞麻籽油，未料商品去年9月入關時卻被查出有大麻成分，劉女被依運輸二級毒品等罪嫌遭送辦，新北地檢署調查認為，產品內容解說均未提及有大麻成分，認定劉女罪嫌不足不起訴。<br />\n<br />\n開庭時，劉女坦承有在網站訂購亞麻籽油，但聲稱因為年紀越來越大，有罹患糖尿病風險，所以開始接觸生酮飲食，加入臉書生酮社團後，團友推薦她喝含有豐富OMEGA3、OMEGA9的食用油，包含亞麻仁油、橄欖油、南瓜籽油等，但在台灣網站與實體商店查價，發現動輒要400、500元，覺得太貴，後來發現美國「iHerb」網站亞麻籽油500ML只要200多元，因此下單購買，她在「iHerb」網站還有購買其他保健食品。<br />\n<br />\n檢方認為，商品收件姓名、地址為真實姓名及住處，劉女並未加以隱匿以躲避查緝，加上商品成分標示未提到含有大麻等成分，且「iHerb」也有販售其他健康食品，採信劉女不知購買油品含有禁藥成分說詞，今將劉女不起訴。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，除了劉女，北台灣另有40多位民眾也因在iHerb網站購買亞麻仁油遭送辦。"},{"pid":"113a2d9e95fb6b5830d8c1224afb0f8c06929a2b","tid":789108,"uid":157362,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T04:18:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c9fbb0bdb55da7e3cf3614c78a3373404f14d552","tid":789108,"uid":4942,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T04:20:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔告iherb?"},{"pid":"d370065b9d86066316ee826c7c53753ea2406557","tid":789108,"uid":13663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T04:22:25.000Z","msg":"iherb好多正野 成日買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"779f619c91ae685476d2a1d81ad04c9f0dd7f495","tid":789108,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T04:23:45.000Z","msg":"台灣人唔識雞腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c7b366a6dbeed04abec3a4b29ea336d648f57f1","tid":789108,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T04:26:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 識玩, 同ebay一樣"},{"pid":"927a0d9737d3e7ef19cc7bd4881beb9e504cec7b","tid":789108,"uid":14423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T04:36:06.000Z","msg":"連登仔瘋狂掃貨"}]}